Hey guys! Steve here to explain this joke. So basically, The joke here is that we associate the number 404 with Errors and the words "Not found" because our browsers, whenever they're unable to load a webpage, show this message "Error 404. Page Not Found". So using that in this meme, when the parents ask the person if they got a job, then they told them "Job 404" which because of the meaning of 404 from browsers would mean "Job Not Found" that this person was still jobless as they couldn't find a job.
